    create sequence BASE_SEQ
    minvalue 1
    maxvalue 9999999999999999999999999999
    start with 101
    increment by 1
    nocache;

Why so happens? I have some entities with PK 51, 52 ... etc, and sequence starting with 101.

AS - GlassFish 3.1.1

